WEBVTT

00:00.343 --> 00:01.714
Previously on One Tree Hill.

00:01.772 --> 00:04.235
I knew this meant a lot to you. I bought it back.

00:06.483 --> 00:07.332
You like her, huh?

00:07.393 --> 00:10.108
Yeah, but guys like me don’t get girls like her.

00:10.169 --> 00:12.436
Felix, you took care of me?

00:12.867 --> 00:13.619
Yeah…

00:15.539 --> 00:17.194
Sometimes you gotta break the rules.

00:19.015 --> 00:22.950
Relax, it’s cool. Peyton and I did a couple of lines the other night. Aint that right Peyton?

00:23.015 --> 00:26.825
You’ve got a good sound… and watching you tonight, I could definitely see us doing something together.

00:26.866 --> 00:28.156
- So you won’t be alone tonight. 
- Nope.

00:28.216 --> 00:31.381
- What’re you gonna do until then? 
- Probably just gonna… hang out with Brooke.

00:31.790 --> 00:37.044
Where do you go when you’re lonely, 
I’ll follow you.

00:37.101 --> 00:40.388
This is… the first time I’ve been in a church since my mom died.

00:41.472 --> 00:43.762
I think about her every day.

00:44.048 --> 00:48.722
Dan has a heart condition known as HCM. It’s a… genetic mutation.

00:48.800 --> 00:50.904
Come on man, what are the odds of us even having this thing anyway?

00:51.001 --> 00:51.918
Fifty-fifty.

00:52.255 --> 00:54.968
I’m sorry. I don’t wanna know.

00:55.194 --> 00:57.196
- You like my sister? 
- You know I do.

00:57.489 --> 00:59.121
Stay the hell away from her.

